    "A high level taxonomy of popular sound synthesis methods, based on the classifications of Schwarz (2007) and Bilbao (2009).",
    "DDSP methods (bold) offer a combination of data-driven and parametric characteristics.",
    "This diagram is illustrative of high level relationships, and is not intended to exhaustively catalogue all audio synthesis techniques.",
